      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, peel and chop (or grate) the <strong>ginger</strong></p>\r\n<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (or wok) over a medium-high heat with 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp]</span> <strong>vegetable oil</strong></p>\r\n<p>Once&nbsp;hot, add the <strong>pork</strong> and <strong>ginger</strong> and cook for 3-4 min or until lightly browned all over</p>",
